Mr. Speaker , being a member of parliament for the great riding of Renfrew - Nipissing - Pembroke and having Canadian forces base Petawawa in my riding , I believe I know what kind of men and women wear the Canadian forces uniform . 
their duty is to defend , protect and , if necessary , engage in the field of battle . 
they are proud of this distinction and have never ever failed to follow that path . 
